| Use | Token |
|-----|-------|
| Neutral bg | `--bg-base-tertiary` |
| Neutral border | `--border-base-default` |
| Neutral text | `--text-base-default` |
| Success light | `--bg-success-tertiary`, `--text-success-default` |
| Success medium | `--bg-success-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Warning light | `--bg-warning-tertiary`, `--text-warning-default` |
| Warning medium | `--bg-warning-default`, `--text-base-default` |
| Error light | `--bg-danger-tertiary`, `--text-danger-default` |
| Error medium | `--bg-danger-default`, `--text-brand-on-brand` |
| Counter | `--bg-brand-tertiary` |

---

## Structure

- **Shape:** Rounded rectangle; Radius/200 or Radius/Full (pill).
- **Padding:** Space/100–200.

---

## Variants (from Figma)

### Loading / placeholder
- **Background:** `--bg-base-tertiary`; border `--border-base-default`.
- **Content:** Spinner icon + "Label..." text.
- **Use:** While content is loading.

### Informational / warning
- **Background:** `--bg-base-tertiary`; border `--border-base-default`.
- **Content:** Exclamation icon + "Label".
- **Use:** Warnings, info callouts.

### Neutral (solid gray)
- **Background:** `--bg-base-tertiary`.
- **Text:** `--text-base-default`.
- **Use:** Neutral labels.

### Color-coded (semantic)
Each: Light, Medium, Dark variation. Small solid circle icon left of "Label".

| Variant | Light | Medium |
|---------|-------|--------|
| Green (success) | `--bg-success-tertiary` bg, `--text-success-default` text | `--bg-success-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text |
| Yellow/Orange (warning) | `--bg-warning-tertiary` bg, `--text-warning-default` text | `--bg-warning-default` bg, `--text-base-default` text |
| Red (error) | `--bg-danger-tertiary` bg, `--text-danger-default` text | `--bg-danger-default` bg, `--text-brand-on-brand` text |

**Icon:** Small solid circle in matching semantic color.

### Counter tag
- **Size:** Small.
- **Background:** `--bg-brand-tertiary`.
- **Text:** "+N" (e.g. "+2"); overflow indicator.
- **Use:** Additional items count beside a tag list.

---

## Implementation guidelines

- Use tokens from `design-system-tokens.mdc` only.
- Do not invent variants; implement only what exists in Figma node 128:10523.
